---
title: Salt & Pepper Beef  with Garlic Rice, Honey-Soy Veggies & Japanese Mayo
description: Watch out salt and pepper squid, because our beef version is going to steal even your biggest fans! With all the
spicy flavour, but pan-fried instead of deep-fried, this is a quick and easy dinner that's going to blow your mind.
